Package: repoquet
Type: Package
Title: Build Self-Auditing Parquet Data Repositories
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Brendan", "Gongol",
    email = "b.gongol@ruhealth.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Brendan Gongol [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Brendan Gongol <b.gongol@ruhealth.org>
Description: A schema-aware, self-auditing engine that transforms heterogeneous
    source files into refreshable, query-ready Parquet repositories for
    larger-than-memory analytics. A metadata-driven workflow combines
    table-specific type normalization, Hive partitioning, source
    fingerprinting, transactional manifests, resumable checkpoints, schema and
    data contracts, catalog generation, reconciliation, custom file readers,
    and validated DuckDB views.
